@port = 3000

### BigCommerce — Test (first 5 products + customers)
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/test/bigcommerce

###

### Shopify — Field Validation (validate all required fields on test product)
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/test/field-validation

###

### Shopify → BigCommerce — Translate Product (map test product to BC shape)
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/test/translate-product

###

### BigCommerce — List Customer Groups
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/bigcommerce/customer-groups

###

### BigCommerce — Create Customer Group
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/bigcommerce/customer-groups
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Master Distro Price",
  "is_default": false
}

###

### BigCommerce — List Categories
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/bigcommerce/categories

###

### BigCommerce — List Brands
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/bigcommerce/brands

###

### BigCommerce — Inventory Locations
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/bigcommerce/inventory/locations

###

### BigCommerce — Inventory Items (all, or filter: ?sku=ABC-001)
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/bigcommerce/inventory/items

###

### BigCommerce — Set Absolute Inventory
PUT http://localhost:{{port}}/api/bigcommerce/inventory/absolute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "sku": "ABC-001", "location_id": 1, "quantity": 50 }
  ]
}

###

### BigCommerce — Relative Inventory Adjustment
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/bigcommerce/inventory/relative
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "items": [
    { "sku": "ABC-001", "location_id": 1, "quantity": -5 }
  ]
}

###

### Migrate Images — Shopify → BigCommerce (replace 123 with real BC product ID)
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/test/migrate-images?bcProductId=123

###

### Migrate Product — Shopify → BigCommerce (sample product)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/migrate/product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "shopifyProductId": "gid://shopify/Product/8191177261119"
}
